text: Maricet Espinosa (born January 2, 1990) is a Cuban judoka. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the women's 63 kg event, in which she was eliminated in the second round by Yarden Gerbi. ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Cuban female judoka Category:Olympic judoka of Cuba Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics
